50|$|The {{goal of the}} {{federation}} is to create cooperation among television archives, multimedia and <b>audiovisual</b> <b>archives</b> and libraries. To meet these goals, FIAT/IFTA provides forums to share knowledge and experience. Some of FIAT/IFTA’s main objectives are to provide a forum for exchange of knowledge and experience between its members, to promote the study of any topic relevant to the {{development and use of}} <b>audiovisual</b> <b>archives</b> and to establish international standards on key issues regarding all aspects of audiovisual media archive management. FIAT/IFTA has over 250 members. The office is currently situated at the Raidió Teilifís Éireann.|$|E
